-- Linc Energy Shares Rise as Company Says Talks on Coal Asset Sale Advancing
-- Tim Smith
-- 2010-08-02T00:36:22Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-08-02/linc-energy-shares-rise-as-company-says-talks-on-coal-asset-sale-advancing.html

          
          
             Linc Energy Ltd. shares rose 9.4
percent in Sydney trading after the company said talks to sell
its coal assets in Queenslannd are at an advanced stage.  
